OL,6,FAfter a two-week validation process
OL,7,Fwhich involved checking the store's
OL,8,FCCTV footage, the incredible win was
OL,9,Fpaid out.
OL,11,FThe couple bought an #8 million estate
OL,12,Fin Perthshire, Scotland, along with a
OL,13,Ffive-bedroom house in Angus and
OL,14,Fpenthouse overlooking the Tay in
OL,15,FDundee, but also used some of their
OL,16,Fmoney to help children with their
OL,17,Fmental health by paying for one of
OL,18,Ftheir friends to get his book, Lucy's
OL,19,FBlue Day published.
