OL,3,CAdvice for lottery winners from a
OL,4,Ccouple who've been there, done that
OL,6,FThe story is about a little girl who
OL,7,Fwakes up one day with blue hair. She
OL,8,Fdiscovers her hair changes colour
OL,9,Fbased on her emotions ` red for angry,
OL,10,Fgreen for envy and blue for sad.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News in the wake of
OL,13,FRichard and Debbie Nuttall's win, Fred
OL,14,Fsaid he was very calm when he realised
OL,15,Fthey'd won the jackpot, which he
OL,16,Fthinks "comes with age", but said his
OL,17,Fwife was "jumping for joy".
