OL,3,CAdvice for lottery winners from a
OL,4,Ccouple who've been there, done that
OL,6,FAsked on why they decided to go public
OL,7,Fwith their win, Fred said: "At first
OL,8,Fwe were hesitant, but then a wonderful
OL,9,FLiverpudlian lady, from the National
OL,10,FLottery, persuaded us to tell our
OL,11,Fstory.
OL,13,F"People want to know who has won all
OL,14,Fthat money, and they will find you
OL,15,Feventually, so we thought we should
OL,16,Fget it out there.
OL,18,F"Camelot, who ran the lottery, were
OL,19,Ffantastic with us, they rang us every
OL,20,Fday to check we were ok, and gave us
OL,21,Fbrilliant support."
