OL,3,CAdvice for lottery winners from a
OL,4,Ccouple who've been there, done that
OL,6,FHe said winning the money had given
OL,7,Fhim and his wife Lesley freedom, and
OL,8,Fmeans they don't have to worry about
OL,9,Feveryday things like bills, but it
OL,10,Fdoes have a number of down sides.
OL,12,FFred said: "If you have any skeletons
OL,13,Fin your closet, the press will dig.
OL,14,FLuckily we didn't but we still get
OL,15,Fpress attention now, with certain
OL,16,Fmedia wanting to know our personal
OL,17,Flife, and what we are spending our
OL,18,Fmoney on.
