OL,3,CAdvice for lottery winners from a
OL,4,Ccouple who've been there, done that
OL,6,F"Sometimes you need to be suspicious
OL,7,Fof people and wary of their motives,
OL,8,Ffor example are people only being nice
OL,9,Fto you so you'll give them some money?
OL,11,F"While I can't advise these new
OL,12,Fwinners on what to do, I can speak
OL,13,Ffrom my experience.
OL,15,F"We bought a few properties and made
OL,16,Fsome investments.
OL,18,F"I would say take your time, don't go
OL,19,Fmad, but do enjoy yourself. Go on the
OL,20,Fholidays you want, buy the car, but be
OL,21,Fcareful and be wary of people."
